{"tid":2111883,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"台積電：9月14日之後不再供貨給華為","createTime":"2020-07-17T01:33:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-17T13:26:55.000Z","uid":48040,"like":82,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"90cf74fcbfd99b76ff72641a53ba68b966f3d882","tid":2111883,"uid":48040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T01:33:07.000Z","msg":"台積電董事長劉德音昨（16）日在線上法說會上宣布，9月14日以後，台積電將不再出貨給華為。不過，劉德音也透露，未來美國政府可能放寬一般產品出貨華為禁令。<br />\n<br />\n華為是台積電第2大客戶，美國政府5月15日發布新的出口規定，要求廠商要用美國製造的設備或依美國軟體與技術設計的晶片供貨華為，必須先取得美方許可證。劉德音指出，當時台積電就已經不再接受華為訂單，9月14日後更將不再出貨華為。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/SomethinkMore/status/1283937355359870976?s=20\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSomethinkMore%2Fstatus%2F1283937355359870976%3Fs%3D20&d=q%2BUwj3SihaKoadPXZHTFaegAExyYYV7WT87CuOwwBqU%3D&h=a834d726\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSomethinkMore%2Fstatus%2F1283937355359870976%3Fs%3D20&h=e89cc626\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/SomethinkMore/status/1283937355359870976?s=20</a>"},{"pid":"a6f2d4b81cf3da3669564632f396d337c83f16fe","tid":2111883,"uid":113187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T01:33:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d79a73668a6ac230466cee3d6a22c502a5d7348f","tid":2111883,"uid":38904,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T01:34:25.000Z","msg":"華為用自己嘅chips咪得<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f974638a9a99c51905446e5b2aa3103bb15d2edd","tid":2111883,"uid":155095,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T01:35:04.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\">未來美國政府可能放寬一般產品出貨華為禁令</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6afa2